@startuml get_building

title GET /buildings e GET /buildings/{id} — Buscar Prédio

actor Client
participant "BuildingController" as Ctrl
participant "GetBuildingUseCase" as UC
participant "BuildingMapper" as Mapper
participant "BuildingRepositoryPort" as Repo
database "buildings" as DB

== Listar todos ==

Client -> Ctrl: GET /buildings
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> UC: findAll()
activate UC

UC -> Repo: findAll()
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM buildings\nWHERE status != DELETED
DB --> Repo: List<Building>
Repo --> UC: List<Building>
deactivate Repo

UC -> Mapper: toResponse(each building)
activate Mapper
Mapper --> UC: List<BuildingResponse>
deactivate Mapper

UC --> Ctrl: List<BuildingResponse>
deactivate UC
Ctrl --> Client: 200 OK {List<BuildingResponse>}
deactivate Ctrl

== Buscar por ID ==

Client -> Ctrl: GET /buildings/{id}
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> UC: findById(id)
activate UC

UC -> Repo: findById(BuildingId.of(id))
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM buildings\nWHERE id=? AND status!=DELETED
DB --> Repo: Optional<Building>
Repo --> UC: Optional<Building>
deactivate Repo

alt not found
  UC --> Ctrl: ResourceNotFoundException
  Ctrl --> Client: 404 Not Found
else found
  UC -> Mapper: toResponse(building)
  activate Mapper
  Mapper --> UC: BuildingResponse
  deactivate Mapper
  UC --> Ctrl: BuildingResponse
  Ctrl --> Client: 200 OK {BuildingResponse}
end

deactivate UC
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml
